My daughter has most of the Dr. Panda games.  They generally provide a high quality, bite-sized experience.  This new firefighting game hits all the right buttons.  It manages to encompass the entire childhood firefighting fantasy, while staying very simple and accessible.  The visuals are also vibrant and well animated.  Performs surprisingly well on my daughter's underpowered Galaxy Tab 4. Highly recommended.
